### Problem09

Please take a look at the following java program:

```java
public class Read
{
    public static void main(String[] args) 
    {
        int a = StdIn.readInt(); 
        int b = StdIn.readInt(); 
        int c = -1;
        int d = 0;

        if (StdIn.readInt()>4){
            c = StdIn.readInt(); 
        }
        if (StdIn.isEmpty()){
            d =StdIn.readInt();
        }

        int e = a + b ; 

    }
}
```

Suppose the content of the file ```data.txt``` is ' 3 2 5 3 1 2 2 2 '. Read.java is already compiled, and StdIn is imported.

We do:

```
java Read < data.txt
```

The value of e is _____(0)\___, and the value of c is _____(1)\___, and the value of d is _____(2)\___.
